                }
            ],
            "text": "Sharing some sources here for those who want to read more!\n\nhttps://t.co/2v0DkNT0EX\n\nhttps://t.co/FdpQMgsnyf\n\nhttps://t.co/ouPzzbSxTJ"
        }
